{"tid":1122015,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"[開估] 一張Display Card點樣同時100%效能玩兩隻game","createTime":"2019-04-23T16:47:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-24T08:50:48.000Z","uid":55725,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9f6a869c1ed173ce5eff60d7da7d07df49357ae3","tid":1122015,"uid":55725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T16:47:02.000Z","msg":"適逄巴黎聖母院大火，都係時候問估當年舊登我點樣串柒啲linux撚，究竟點樣1張display card 100%效能同時開兩隻unity一齊玩?<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=6656463&amp;page=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Fmessage%3D6656463%26page%3D1&d=zdm3SfM4sEUVnXmiquxubHRNzM9MViFDfs2457H6WAQ%3D&h=112fed52\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=6656463&amp;page=1</a><br />\n<br />\nRequirement<br />\n1. <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1</span>張display card，我個張係980ti，愈多vram愈好<br />\n2. SoftXpand<br />\n3. Windows 7，要有兩個user account<br />\n4. 兩set keyboard mouse，兩個mon，一個插HDMI，一個插DVI<br />\n5. Sandboxie，用嚟解決steam雙開問題<br />\n<br />\nSteps<br />\n1. 裝晒要裝嘅野，sandboxie要set啱野，SoftXpand要set啱野<br />\n2. 開著部機，兩set keyboard mouse分別跟兩個mon，user1入第1個windows account，user2入第2個windows account<br />\n3. user1開正常steam，user2開sandboxie steam，跟住之後好多game都可以雙開一齊玩，前提係steam要買兩份，user1係我嘅正常account所以無開sandboxie，SoftXpand最貴個隻版本理論上係support到10幾個user同時瘋狂開word, excel, powerpoint, cs, pubg......<br />\n所以我係可以一邊打機，另一半瘋狂睇AV<br />\n<br />\n講到呢到，唔知linux撚而家做到9成效能未?<br />\n又要isolation高又要高效能，我都想學下野點做，不過windows真係賤格啦，原來係可以同時開幾隻game幾個applications幾個人一齊玩，真係唔明點解microsoft唔開放呢啲功能，應該係錢作怪<br />\n<img src=\"https://neato4u.files.wordpress.com/2013/02/x11.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fneato4u.files.wordpress.com%2F2013%2F02%2Fx11.png&h=41bc7423&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d2d98694f013371457870d9e57f34f303eafa8b2","tid":1122015,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T19:56:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: blue